{
  "stem": "22391.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my father was there already waiting for us-- and they shouldn't find out that we disappeared from the ghetto somehow.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was not supposed to be told.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, but I think because he was so close with my father that he was the one.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when I went back to Hungary, when he saw me, he said, listen, your father and mother left a little jewelry here and you come pick it up.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I assume, whatever information came, it came from him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandfather was in a different [NON-ENGLISH] in [NON-ENGLISH] because from Beled, they took everybody to Sopron, to another ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were in Szombathely because they don't want him to know that we left.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were in Szombathely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But somehow, from Szombathely, they had a chance to go to Sopron.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we went to Sopron, hoping that we're going to find our grandfather there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my grandfather was there, but we never saw him because he was still between the hospital group that they took from [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and they don't let us go see anybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we didn't see him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The only time I really saw my grandfather when we got to Auschwitz-Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Over there--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was with us, from Szombathely to Sopron.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything was in short time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I never know dates.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember dates.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what I could tell you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, exactly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We wasn't told everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't even know if my parents know everything, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's-- we were all hoping that it was just temporary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember at one point, the two German men came and they said, well, if you want to stay together as family, you come forward and come with me.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father said, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
